    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@value": "The supports property is a transitive relation between DigitalObjects entailed by its subproperty, directlySupports, which is non-transitive. In EvidenceGraphs, if A supports B, then the correctness (truth value) of A provides a warrant for belief in the correctness (truth value) of B."
