      "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@value": "The endTime of something. For a reserved event or service (e.g. FoodEstablishmentReservation), the time that it is expected to end. For actions that span a period of time, when the action was performed. e.g. John wrote a book from January to December. For media, including audio and video, it's the time offset of the end of a clip within a larger file.\n\nNote that Event uses startDate/endDate instead of startTime/endTime, even when describing dates with times. This situation may be clarified in future revisions."
      }
    ],
